snippet.title: Fire Emblem Warriors: Three Hopes - Announcement Trailer  - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Pre-order now: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/fire-emblem-warriors-three-hopes-switch/

Prepare for a different story set in the same universe as #FireEmblem: Three Houses with Edelgard, Dimitri, and Claude in Fire Emblem Warriors: Three Hopes, arriving to Nintendo Switch on 6/24!

#FireEmblemWarriors #NintendoDirect #NintendoSwitch
